headline: Jim Cramer Says “I Don’t Want to Own Synchrony, I Want to Own Capital One”
summary: Synchrony Financial (NYSE:SYF) is one of the stocks Jim Cramer commented on. Answering a caller’s query about the stock, Cramer remarked: I don’t want to own Synchrony.
